name: 08 Memory Card - Yan & Chilli
description: Come to the mini restaurant at the end of the road near the bodhi tree, Resto Yan! Selected seasonings are imported from all over the district, prepared with the right composition of spices and full of love. Cuisine that will make you yearn to come back to Yami district. The mainstay menu is Nasi Padang and Grilled Jellyfish with Mandarin sauce. Yan the chef is friendly and kind and has an assistant named Chilli. She is an agile and sprightful employee!
